org.omg.DynamicAny

Interface DynEnum

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DynAny, DynAnyOperations, DynEnumOperations, IDLEntity, Object, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    _DynEnumStub

    public interface DynEnum
extends DynEnumOperations, DynAny, IDLEntity
    DynEnum objects support the manipulation of IDL enumerated values. The current position of a DynEnum is always -1.
